In [18]:
for region in regions:
    df = data[data["Rgion"] == region]
    df = df.set_index("Anne", drop=True).sort_values("Anne")
    df["Parc install olien (MW)"].plot()
    plt.xlabel("Year")
    plt.ylabel("Installed (MW)")
    plt.title(f"Wind Power Capacity by Region over the years")
    plt.legend(regions)
In [19]:
for region in regions:
    df = data[data["Rgion"] == region]
    df = df.set_index("Anne", drop=True).sort_values("Anne")
    df["Parc install olien (MW)"].plot()
    plt.xlabel("Year")
    plt.ylabel("Installed (MW)")
    plt.title(f"Installed for region : {region}")
    plt.show()
